{"tha-ap433:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap433:0.2":"Ekaviharivagga ","tha-ap433:0.3":"1 Ekaviharikattheraapadana ","tha-ap433:1.1":"“Imamhi bhaddake kappe, ","tha-ap433:1.2":"brahmabandhu mahayaso; ","tha-ap433:1.3":"Kassapo nama gottena, ","tha-ap433:1.4":"uppajji vadatam varo. ","tha-ap433:2.1":"Nippapanco niralambo, ","tha-ap433:2.2":"akasasamamanaso; ","tha-ap433:2.3":"Sunnatabahulo tadi, ","tha-ap433:2.4":"animittarato vasi. ","tha-ap433:3.1":"Asangacitto nikleso, ","tha-ap433:3.2":"asamsattho kule gane; ","tha-ap433:3.3":"Mahakaruniko viro, ","tha-ap433:3.4":"vinayopayakovido. ","tha-ap433:4.1":"Uyyutto parakiccesu, ","tha-ap433:4.2":"vinayanto sadevake; ","tha-ap433:4.3":"Nibbanagamanam maggam, ","tha-ap433:4.4":"gatim pankavisosanam. ","tha-ap433:5.1":"Amatam paramassadam, ","tha-ap433:5.2":"jaramaccunivaranam; ","tha-ap433:5.3":"Mahaparisamajjhe so, ","tha-ap433:5.4":"nisinno lokatarako. ","tha-ap433:6.1":"Karavikaruto natho, ","tha-ap433:6.2":"brahmaghoso tathagato; ","tha-ap433:6.3":"Uddharanto mahadugga, ","tha-ap433:6.4":"vippanatthe anayake. ","tha-ap433:7.1":"Desento virajam dhammam, ","tha-ap433:7.2":"dittho me lokanayako; ","tha-ap433:7.3":"Tassa dhammam sunitvana, ","tha-ap433:7.4":"pabbajim anagariyam. ","tha-ap433:8.1":"Pabbajitva tadapaham, ","tha-ap433:8.2":"cintento jinasasanam; ","tha-ap433:8.3":"Ekakova vane ramme, ","tha-ap433:8.4":"vasim samsaggapilito. ","tha-ap433:9.1":"Sakkayavupakaso me, ","tha-ap433:9.2":"hetubhuto mamabhavi; ","tha-ap433:9.3":"Manaso vupakasassa, ","tha-ap433:9.4":"samsaggabhayadassino. ","tha-ap433:10.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap433:10.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap433:10.3":"Nagova bandhanam chetva, ","tha-ap433:10.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap433:11.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap433:11.2":"mama buddhassa santike; ","tha-ap433:11.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","tha-ap433:11.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap433:12.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap433:12.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap433:12.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap433:12.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap433:13.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ekavihariko thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap433:14.1":"Ekaviharikattherassapadanam pathamam. "}